Detailed Description

Class containing the map used for routing.

Contains node and connection data and external nodes and connections (connections to another maps).
NB! If mc2 is not compiled with -D_REENTRANT=1, the loading of maps will not be threadsafe and the constructor will read outside the DataBuffer sent from MapModule.}
FIXME: Allocate all the connections at once when loading the map. The problem is that the connections and nodes etc. must know if they are created in the map or elsewhere (copies) and behave differently in their destructors in the different cases.
